data.description: Near new custom home, luxury appliances and finishes with upgrades throughout, oversized 2 car garage, covered back patio and large brick wall enclosed back yard with RV gates/parking, no HOA,  an expansive great room, thoughtful split floorplan, high ceilings, large windows, and custom architectural touches every room will impress. From white quartz waterfall island and countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms to match, to the custom crafted cabinets with soft close doors and drawers, upgraded windows, doors, and flooring, stainless steel appliances. The primary suite has a custom walk in stone shower, an oversized walk in closet and double sinks in white quartz, walk in pantry and separate laundry room near the garage. Located in Mayfield Ranch Estates, a quiet neighborhood, with mountain views near the gorgeous Simkins Park. The  Park has sport fields/court, dog park, playground, facilities completing this perfect home, quiet side of beautiful Pahrump Valley & minutes from downtown.
